"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"recmAUAIwW85ajksn","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"rec6V51IWkgvAcnOU","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"recgdvRbWEPMp5I0z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"recvt2PQbAxcUQYmR","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recyB1eDDoBeVm0Mt","target":"recaHkhAvEICQr7fB","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recHWL6HXBkjzygqE","ref":"Ps.68.1","text":"Let God arise, let his enemies be scattered: let them also that hate him flee before him.","year":-1042},{"id":"recjh4aXeSg6rJQC2","ref":"Ps.68.2","text":"As smoke is driven away, so drive them away: as wax melteth before the fire, so let the wicked perish at the presence of God.","year":-1042},{"id":"recn28XvhaFZuKVKx","ref":"Ps.68.3","text":"But let the righteous be glad; let them rejoice before God: yea, let them exceedingly rejoice.","year":-1042},{"id":"rec0wrAqlSMTxYlK4","ref":"Ps.68.4","text":"Sing unto God, sing praises to his name: extol him that rideth upon the heavens by his name JAH, and rejoice before him.","year":-1042},{"id":"rectUls24qXetDRQq","ref":"Ps.68.5","text":"A father of the fatherless, and a judge of the widows, is God in his holy habitation.","year":-1042},{"id":"recHTSaESPPifFK6I","ref":"Ps.68.6","text":"God setteth the solitary in families: he bringeth out those which are bound with chains: but the rebellious dwell in a dry land.","year":-1042},{"id":"recCpC6NaPws8DiDE","ref":"Ps.68.7","text":"O God, when thou wentest forth before thy people, when thou didst march through the wilderness; Selah:","year":-1042},{"id":"recNKPqvErZfhhc8i","ref":"Ps.68.8","text":"The earth shook, the heavens also dropped at the presence of God: even Sinai itself was moved at the presence of God, the God of Israel.","year":-1042}]}
